title: Top things to do in Queensland
text:
Top things to do in Queensland Christina Pfeiffer | 24th Jul 2015 4:08 PM Christina Pfeiffer   
When it comes to travelling, there are so many wonderful experiences on offer around the world. I want to do them all. Of course, I realise there's just not enough time for anyone to experience everything on their bucket list. 
As a keen traveller, I'm also a collector of bucket lists. My iPhone notepad is full of places I plan to visit one day. I also love to bookmark lists of fun and amazing things to do while travelling. 
When it comes to fun activities, I'll have to say Queensland comes out tops. And as a Queensland who is passionate about the state, my Queensland bucket list keeps growing and growing. 
I'd love to know how many other Queenslanders enjoy exploring close to home.
